title: CREATION OF UNIVERSE [Web site]
description: The Universe and its elements : all the galaxies, stars, planets, asteroids, the Milky Way, the Sun, the Earth, the Moon and billions of other immense bodies are rotating and revolving in excellent harmony. If scrutinized in terms of cosmic, physical, mathematical and bio-chemical aspects, from micro level to macro level, the Universe proves to be supplied with the most suitable design for human life. This web site displays the evidence for the creation of the Universe and it reveals the eternal might and wisdom of Allah, who created this great universe from nothingness.
